{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":989722,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":84506796,"nickname":"脂肪骨","uptime":1542870265452},"lrc":{"version":27,"lyric":"{\"t\":-1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Adam Levine\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/6x5iGh25AfJkA_FN0g6Arg==/5917571581031334.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=196215&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Benjamin Levin\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Ammar Malik\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Dan Omelio\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Shellback\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Cameron Thomaz\"}]}\n{\"t\":-500,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Adam Levine\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/6x5iGh25AfJkA_FN0g6Arg==/5917571581031334.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=196215&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Benjamin Levin\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Ammar Malik\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Dan Omelio\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Shellback\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Cameron Thomaz\"}]}\n[00:00.000]作曲 : Adam Levine/Benjamin Levin/Ammar Malik/Dan Omelio/Shellback/Cameron Thomaz\n[00:00.360]作词 : Adam Levine/Benjamin Levin/Ammar Malik/Dan Omelio/Shellback/Cameron Thomaz\n[00:01.080]I'm at a payphone trying to call home\n[00:04.280]All of my change I spent on you\n[00:08.590]Where have the times gone\n[00:10.670]Baby it's all wrong, where are the plans we made for two?\n[00:17.540]Yeah, I, I know it's hard to remember\n[00:19.880]The people we used to be\n[00:23.130]It's even harder to picture\n[00:25.300]That you're not here next to me\n[00:27.520]You say it's too late to make it\n[00:29.890]But is it too late to try?\n[00:31.880]And in our time that you wasted\n[00:33.600]All of our bridges burned down\n[00:35.830]I've wasted my nights\n[00:37.960]You turned out the lights\n[00:40.970]Now I'm paralyzed\n[00:42.700]Still stuck in that time when we called it love\n[00:47.350]But even the sun sets in paradise\n[00:50.550]I'm at a payphone trying to call home\n[00:57.080]All of my change I spent on you\n[01:00.790]Where have the times gone\n[01:03.740]Baby it's all wrong, where are the plans we made for two?\n[01:09.400]If happy ever after did exist\n[01:11.130]I would still be holding you like this\n[01:18.330]All those fairytales are full of shit\n[01:22.540]One more ****ing love song i'll be sick\n[01:25.530]You turned your back on tomorrow\n[01:30.730]Cause you forgot yesterday\n[01:31.700]I gave you my love to borrow\n[01:34.650]But you just gave it away\n[01:37.390]You can't expect me to be fine\n[01:39.730]I don't expect you to care\n[01:41.770]I know I've said it before\n[01:43.590]But all of our bridges burned down\n[01:45.780]I've wasted my nights\n[01:48.860]You turned out the lights\n[01:51.030]Now I'm paralyzed\n[01:53.270]Still stuck in that time when we called it love\n[01:57.380]But even the sun sets in paradise\n[02:00.170]I'm at a payphone trying to call home\n[02:06.670]All of my change I spent on you\n[02:10.580]Where have the times gone\n[02:12.860]Baby it's all wrong, where are the plans we made for two?\n[02:19.300]If happy ever after did exist\n[02:21.050]I would still be holding you like this\n[02:28.100]All those fairytales are full of bullshit\n[02:32.470]One more ****ing love song i'll be sick\n[02:36.720]Now I'm at a payphone...\n[02:39.160]Wiz Khalifa\n[02:39.470]Man **** that bullshit\n[02:40.380]I'll be out spending all this money while you sitting round\n[02:42.230]Wondering why it wasn't you who came up from nothing\n[02:44.010]Made it from the bottom\n[02:45.020]Now when you see me I'm stunning\n[02:46.490]And all of my cars start with the push of a button\n[02:49.270]Telling me the chances since I blew up or whatever you call it\n[02:50.890]Switched the number to my phone\n[02:52.590]So you never could call it\n[02:53.700]Don't need my name on my show\n[02:55.680]You can tell it I'm ballin'\n[02:55.980]Swish, what a shame could have got picked\n[02:58.050]Had a really good game but you missed your last shot\n[02:59.890]So you talk about who you see at the top\n[03:02.670]Or what you could've saw\n[03:02.770]But sad to say it's over for\n[03:04.190]Phantom pulled up valet open doors\n[03:05.460]Wiz like go away, got what you was looking for\n[03:07.250]Now it's me who they want\n[03:09.820]So you can go and take that little piece of shit with you\n[03:11.600]I'm at a payphone trying to call home\n[03:16.910]All of my change I spent on you\n[03:20.260]Where have the times gone\n[03:22.580]Baby it's all wrong, where are the plans we made for two?\n[03:28.950]If happy ever after did exist\n[03:33.510]I would still be holding you like this\n[03:37.990]All these fairytales are full of bullshit\n[03:42.240]One more ****ing love song i'll be sick\n[03:45.330]Now I'm at a Payphone\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":17,"lyric":"[00:00.000]\n[00:00.360]\n[00:01.080]我在电话亭里尝试给你打电话\n[00:04.280]为了打给你，我花光了所有的零钱。\n[00:08.590]我们好久都没见面了。\n[00:10.670]宝贝 一切都错了，我们的二人世界的计划哪去了？\n[00:17.540]是的 我知道很难去记住\n[00:19.880]曾经的我们是什么样的。\n[00:23.130]但更难的是去想象\n[00:25.300]你会不在我身边。\n[00:27.520]你说已经太晚无法挽回\n[00:29.890]但是，这太晚了吗？\n[00:31.880]你浪费了，我们在一起的时间。\n[00:33.600]我们的一切都已崩塌\n[00:35.830]我浪费了那些夜晚\n[00:37.960]你熄灭了灯火\n[00:40.970]我已全身麻痹，动弹不得。\n[00:42.700]我还停留在，我们称于爱的时光。\n[00:47.350]即使天堂的太阳都已经落下\n[00:50.550]我仍在电话亭里尝试给你打电话\n[00:57.080]为了打给你，我花光了所有的零钱。\n[01:00.790]我们好久都没见面了。\n[01:03.740]宝贝儿 一切都已经不对，我们的二人世界的计划哪去了？\n[01:09.400]如果快乐的生活的确存在过。\n[01:11.130]我还会这样拥抱你\n[01:18.330]所有的童话都是骗人的\n[01:22.540]再听到那该死的情歌我可能会吐\n[01:25.530]你已经不想再回头\n[01:30.730]因为你已忘记了过去\n[01:31.700]我给你我全部的爱\n[01:34.650]但是你依然弃之不顾\n[01:37.390]你不在乎我的死活\n[01:39.730]我也不期望你的关怀\n[01:41.770]我知道这是旧事重提\n[01:43.590]但属于我们的一切都已经崩裂\n[01:45.780]我荒废了我的夜晚\n[01:48.860]你熄灭了灯火\n[01:51.030]我全身麻痹 动弹不得\n[01:53.270]我还停留在，我们称于爱的时光。\n[01:57.380]即使天堂的太阳都已经落下\n[02:00.170]我电话亭里尝试给你打电话\n[02:06.670]为了打给你，我花光了所有的零钱。\n[02:10.580]我们好久都没见面了。\n[02:12.860]宝贝儿 一切都错了，我们的二人世界的计划哪去了？\n[02:19.300]如果快乐的生活的确存在过。\n[02:21.050]我还会这样拥抱你\n[02:28.100]所有的童话都是骗人的\n[02:32.470]再听到那该死的情歌我可能会吐\n[02:36.720]我电话亭里尝试给你打电话......\n[02:39.160]WOW\n[02:39.470]我去\n[02:40.380]我会在外头拼命花钱，而你却坐在那里琢磨\n[02:42.230]为什么白手起家的那个人不是你。\n[02:44.010]从空白里再次奋斗\n[02:45.020]当你会发现如今的我气派不凡\n[02:46.490]看看这些罕见的名车，都只需按键就可启动。\n[02:49.270]我发生奇迹之后他们都说我变了，懒得听他们叽叽歪歪。\n[02:50.890]换掉我的号码\n[02:52.590]那样你就无法再拨打它\n[02:53.700]我的名字，不提我大名你也知道\n[02:55.680]我就是这么牛X\n[02:55.980]啧 你错过了那些真是耻辱。\n[02:58.050]你完美的玩了整个游戏 却玩废了最后一击\n[02:59.890]所以你不停的说着 你曾经的光荣。\n[03:02.670]或者，你本来可以得到些什么 。\n[03:02.770]但必须说的是 那都结束了。\n[03:04.190]劳斯莱斯幻影停了下来侍者打开车门\n[03:05.460]都离开吧 你得到了一直想要的\n[03:07.250]现在他们需要的是我了\n[03:09.820]所以你可以滚了 带着你的蠢玩意儿。\n[03:11.600]我电话亭里尝试给你打电话。\n[03:16.910]为了打给你，我花光了所有的零钱。\n[03:20.260]我们好久都没见面了。\n[03:22.580]宝贝儿 一切都错了，我们的二人世界的计划哪去了？\n[03:28.950]如果快乐的生活的确存在过。\n[03:33.510]我还会这样拥抱你\n[03:37.990]所有的童话都是骗人的\n[03:42.240]再听到那该死的情歌我可能会吐\n[03:45.330]我电话亭里尝试给你打电话......"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":24,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Adam Levine\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/6x5iGh25AfJkA_FN0g6Arg==/5917571581031334.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=196215&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Benjamin Levin\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Ammar Malik\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Dan Omelio\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Shellback\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Cameron Thomaz\"}]}\n{\"t\":45,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Adam Levine\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/6x5iGh25AfJkA_FN0g6Arg==/5917571581031334.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=196215&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Benjamin Levin\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Ammar Malik\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Dan Omelio\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Shellback\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Cameron Thomaz\"}]}\n[90,1860](90,97,0)作(187,97,0)曲 (284,97,0): (381,97,0)Adam (478,97,0)Levine(575,97,0)/(672,97,0)Benjamin (769,97,0)Levin(866,97,0)/(963,97,0)Ammar (1060,97,0)Malik(1157,97,0)/(1254,97,0)Dan (1351,97,0)Omelio(1448,97,0)/(1545,97,0)Shellback(1642,97,0)/(1739,97,0)Cameron (1836,114,0)Thomaz\n[1950,18